text: Dalel Singh Ror is an Indian volleyball player who received one of the country's highest sporting honours, the Arjuna Award, in 1990. Dalel Singh was born on 10 June 1956 in Amin village near Kurukshetra, in Haryana.Page 253, Students' Britannica India, by Dale Hoiberg, Indu Ramchandani, Popular Prakashan India, ==References== Category:Living people Category:1956 births Category:Volleyball players Category:People from Haryana
